; ● 1个100M Ethernet接口 　　<br />\r\n&nbsp; ● SD，MMC和SDIO接口，最高支持SD 2.0, SDIO 1.1和MMC 4.2传输协议 　　<br />\r\n&nbsp;&nbsp;● I2C，SPI，UART，I2S和S/PDIF接口 　　<br />\r\n&nbsp; ● Flip-Chip BGA封装，23mmx23mm 　　<br />\r\n&nbsp; ● 芯片典型工作功耗小于2W&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<span style=\"font-size:small;\"><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span style=\"color:#266abd;\"><span class=\"STYLE17\"><span class=\"STYLE37\"><span style=\"color:#000000;\"><span style=\"color:#525252;\"><span style=\"font-size:small;\"><span class=\"STYLE17\"><span class=\"STYLE37\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><strong>典型系统结构图：<br />\r\n</strong></span></span><span style=\"font-size:small;\"><strong><span><span><span style=\"color:#266abd;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\r\n</span></span></span></strong></span><strong><span class=\"STYLE17\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.nufrontsoft.com/UploadFiles/image/%E6%97%A0%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98.bmp\" height=\"390\" width=\"554\" /><br />\r\n</span></strong></span></span></span></span></span></span>','{}',NULL,NULL,NULL,'HtmlComponent'),(1328104190046,0,NULL,NULL,0,NULL,'{}',NULL,NULL,NULL,'NavComponent'),(1328104190046,0,'快速导航',NULL,3,'1328104190035','{}',NULL,NULL,NULL,'ArticleListComponent'),(1328104190046,1,NULL,NULL,3,NULL,'{}',NULL,NULL,NULL,'CopyRightComponent'),(1328104190046,0,'关于作者',NULL,4,'linktone，朱瑞贤，男，80后。<br />\n2008北京邮电大学计算机学院毕业后&nbsp; java工程师<br />\n2012 – 至今，android开发工程师<a title=\"豆瓣\" href=\"http://douban.com\" target=\"_blank\"></a><p></p>\n<strong>联系我<br />\nEmail：zhurx4g@gmail.com</strong>','{}',NULL,NULL,NULL,'HtmlComponent'),(1328104190047,1,'公司地址',NULL,4,'北京市海淀区中关村东路1号院8号楼启迪科技大厦B','{\"height\":300,\"width\":710}',NULL,NULL,NULL,'MapComponent'),(1328104190047,0,NULL,NULL,3,NULL,'{}',NULL,NULL,NULL